window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Braxton Thorpe has discovered a threat to the entire solar system, but he has a problem: he's dead.</p> <p>Frozen at death, he awakens to find himself uploaded into an electronic matrix. Exploring beyond the matrix and the larger GlobalNet, he discovers the Oort, a distributed electronic entity older than humanity, with an unnerving secret: Aliens wiped out nearly all life on Earth once, and are coming back to do it again.</p> <p>The mathematical entity that is Thorpe has to find a way to convince humans of the threat, and in time to do something about it. But how, and what?</p> <p>If you've read Niven's<i> A World Out of Time</i> or Taylor's <i>We Are Legion</i>, the opening of <i>Icicle </i>will only seem familiar. Buckle up for a wild ride; you ain't seen nothing.</p>"; 
